data.description: Welcome to your updated, ground-level condo at Sunpointe at Lakewood Estates! Built in 1997, this unit is beautiful, bright and ready to call home. This condo boasts brand new carpet and paint throughout. Modern, updated finishes include light fixtures, faucets, appliances and more. Central air conditioning new in 2018. Water heater new in 2021. All kitchen appliances new in 2021. Washer and dryer new in 2022. Even the staging furniture is negotiable as a separate sale; all you need to do is move in and enjoy! Reserved parking spot directly in front of unit and detached garage a few steps away. This peaceful complex features mature trees, plenty of visitor parking, community pool and community patio/firepit area. Close proximity to Green Gables, retail on Wadsworth and the Belmar Shopping Center. Central location minutes to Hwy 285/6th Ave/1-70/Golden!
